{"tid":458877,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"梁 詠 琪 要 囡 囡 做 灰 姑 娘","createTime":"2017-11-05T09:40:18.000Z","updateTime":"2017-11-05T10:50:44.000Z","uid":35964,"like":2,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"f05509d9f33665bbd83a315ede5c225fab177bfd","tid":458877,"uid":35964,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-05T09:40:18.000Z","msg":"梁詠琪（GiGi）昨日到中環ifc為品牌Aigle新店擔任揭幕嘉賓，獲混血小朋友送上精美鞋履用品。GiGi自稱執篋達人，一家大細外遊所有旅行用品都由她負責，自己屬於穩陣型，連小朋友張被、枕頭都會帶。<br />\nGiGi透露囡囡愛襯衫和公主服，但她卻拒絕買公主服給囡囡Sofia，她說：「大個啲先，唔想佢細細個就以為自己真係公主，要畀佢知道做公主都要執嘢洗碗，灰姑娘都要掃地，要學習優點。」Sofia現在兩歲半，GiGi會陪女兒睇中文書，着重混血囡囡學習中文；她認為沖涼就是親子時間，更是兩母女講中文講得最多的時刻。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20171102/large/02ec1p51.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20171102%2Flarge%2F02ec1p51.jpg&h=4493fb3d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\nGiGi見到混血小朋友即流露慈母般的笑容。"},{"pid":"c257674bee92131efde6bb19da1a898b22a60a40","tid":458877,"uid":57700,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-05T10:02:21.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"57dcca2f8414b610ce6c1086d0d7decca5045b60","tid":458877,"uid":140678,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-05T10:40:19.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>個女好似蝻</blockquote><br />\n樓上好似盲"},{"pid":"637f799b5d1fec604a809eaab12515d795af7eb0","tid":458877,"uid":100136,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-05T10:50:44.000Z","msg":"西班牙籍老公Sergio"}]}